    <h1>Green Hosting SEO: Does It Affect Rankings in 2026?</h1>
    <p class="description">Green hosting SEO is not a direct ranking factor, but it improves Core Web Vitals, uptime, and user trust. Here is what actually moves the needle.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">SG</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
